column2: The Consular Elections are beginning once again, who will you vote for?
You have won the Consular elections and recieved first Facses. Your co-Consul is [consul_2.GetBestName].
You have won the Consular elections, however your co-Consul, [consul_1.GetBestName], has received first Facses.
This years Consular elections have come to a close, the winners are [consul_1.GetBestName] and [consul_2.GetBestName]. [consul_1.GetBestName] has received the honor of first Facses.
